replies.body:
So, this post was 2 years ago. The IFS has been in effect for over 5 years now. The bolded bit is actual code, that an automated system would use.

>Reports haven't lost weight since the instant feedback system was put in place.

>It's actually really simple.

>**if (reports > 0) {
review();
}**

>Riot Tantram (NA) Software Architect  - 2 years ago
That was the old system. 3 years ago? We have since then iterated many times that only one report is needed to flag games.
